{"type": "article", "id": 12989, "title": "木制自行车", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-04T12:17:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 52, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702171820ns3GNB2MpI1hFVkb.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t原始的自行车据说就是木制车，现在兜兜转转，人们又开始对木制自行车感兴趣。近日，法国设计工作室 Keim 和 Breitfuss Workshop 合作推出了 Arvak Bicycle，“Arvak” 据说是北欧神话中的一匹马，象征如太阳般的活力。整辆车全部使用手工打造，质量只有 7.5 公斤，遵循极简主义风格，整个车身零件不超过 20 个，兼具艺术性和实用性。这辆车目前限量生产，<a href=\"http://www.keim-edition.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以尝试预定。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140634wnitC1VyeImslBgk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.89814815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140635wAmPBvlIh2JeKfXg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.00648148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140635D7so8cC9kgPVFaeW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140636jG9ex0kMotb2KQqw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.37988827\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140637u5AENPIaikg37nOR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.08610568\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}